Variance of \(hat{\beta_u}\) and \(hat{\beta_v}\) ordered by column major

Source: R/utilities.R
rate_betauv_two_stage.Rd

Variance of \(hat{\beta_u}\) and \(hat{\beta_v}\) ordered by column major

rate_betauv_two_stage(
  X,
  u,
  v,
  beta0,
  d,
  sigmay2,
  sigmaa2,
  n,
  output = "uv",
  verbose = F
)

Arguments

X

design matrix X
u

u vector
v

v vector
beta0

beta vector
d

d
sigmay2

sigma_y^2
sigmaa2

sigma_a^2
n

number of nodes
output

"uv", "u", "v" to select output for \(beta_u\) and/or \(beta_v\)
verbose

print first and second term of the rate

Value

A vector of rariance for \(hat{\beta_u}\) and \(hat{\beta_v}\)
